况、用户评价、曾获荣誉等作虚假或者引人误解的商业宣传，欺骗、误导消费者”规定，对其处以罚款40万元。雅诗兰黛因虚假宣传被罚40万 - 经济观察网 － 专业财经新闻网站"},"attached_info":"Cj8Io8z6v4Pj/8QIEAMaCDY2NDEwNTg3ILWR54YGMA04vgZAJ3IJNDY4NTg4NjkzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"36 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-cc46a8f74c404c05c7cd3cbe419a68c9_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"40_1625019938.0830302","card_id":"Q_468354788","target":{"id":468354788,"title":"怎么看待马嘉祺后援会自爆粉丝集资 700 万给公司？可能涉及哪些问题？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/468354788","type":"question","created":1624836682,"answer_count":246,"follower_count":995,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[215,1138,8456,168789,210457],"comment_count":52,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"日前，马嘉祺后援会发布一则长文，透露2019年出道战前夕，马嘉祺粉丝在不被看好的情况下曾艰难拼凑700万，拱手交给公司时代峰峻，只望得到公司自己许下的承诺，如今在马嘉祺艰难时刻，却被公司划清界限，粉丝质问公司“为何不敢实践这诺言？为何如今还反捅他一刀”，目前该长文已删除。"},"attached_info":"Cj8Io8z6v4Pj/8QIEAMaCDY2MzU4NTg5IMqU5IYGMDQ44wdAKHIJNDY4MzU0Nzg4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"34 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-5dc68562c590cf2f42309a3a0d5e9454_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"41_1625019938.0835967","card_id":"Q_315066488","target":{"id":315066488,"title":"有没有一刻，突然平静地想离婚？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/315066488","type":"question","created":1552020457,"answer_count":919,"follower_count":3039,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[748,32489],"comment_count":11,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Io8z6v4Pj/8QIEAMaCDMyMjkxNDIxIOnnh+QFMAs43xdAKXIJMzE1MDY2NDg4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"24 万热